  background: {fileID: 0}
  lines:
  - speakerName: "V\u0169"
    englishSpeakerName: Vu
    text: "M\u00E8o \u1EDF \u0111\u00E2u v\u1EADy !!!"
    englishText: Where is that cat?!
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
  - speakerName: "V\u0169"
    englishSpeakerName: Vu
    text: "Nay ng\u00E0y ngh\u1EC9 m\u00E0 sao m\u00E8o m\u00E9o meo v\u1EADy !!!"
    englishText: It's my day off, why is a cat meowing like that?!
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
  - speakerName: "V\u0169"
    englishSpeakerName: Vu
    text: "Phi\u1EC1n qu\u00E1 h\u00E0 ! M\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 gi\u1EA5c"
    englishText: So annoying! There goes my sleep.
    portrait: {fileID: -4254258901546231152, guid: c5d997eca51e38d418373f1e8fdc90ce, type: 3}
